  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate quality of life, sleep and fadigue in patients with
      chronic pain using an Item-Response Theory methodology and also generating a Computer
      Adaptive Testing System
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
